<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 03:15:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>俄新社报道，中国海警船抵达俄罗斯参加联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-coast-guard-ships-arrive-russia-joint-drills-ria-reports-2024-09-17/</link><description>据俄新社周二报道，中国海警船梅山号和秀山号已抵达俄罗斯远东港口符拉迪沃斯托克，与俄罗斯海警船进行联合演习和巡逻。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 02:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-coast-guard-ships-arrive-russia-joint-drills-ria-reports-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国批准向台湾出售价值约2.28亿美元的零部件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-approves-possible-military-sale-taiwan-spare-parts-about-228-mln-2024-09-17/</link><description>美国国务院周一表示，已批准向台湾出售价值约2.28亿美元的外国军事备件，台湾军方表示，这将有助于在面对中国灰色地带入侵时保持战备状态。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 02:11:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-approves-possible-military-sale-taiwan-spare-parts-about-228-mln-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市暂定；美元、收益率因美联储大幅降息而受压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-17/</link><description>亚洲股市周二波动，美元和美国国债收益率承压，距离美联储宽松周期的预期开始仅剩一天，政策制定者可能会大幅降息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 01:31:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>高盛重申看涨金价，因美联储降息希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/goldman-sachs-reiterates-bullish-view-gold-prices-amid-fed-rate-cut-hopes-2024-09-16/</link><description>高盛周一重申了对金价的乐观前景，理由是央行的需求以及美联储在本周的政策会议上即将降息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 23:30:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/goldman-sachs-reiterates-bullish-view-gold-prices-amid-fed-rate-cut-hopes-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鸽派美联储目光，中国通货紧缩力量加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-16/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 21:48:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>帕拉西奥斯最后时刻的进球帮助艾因队在亚冠联赛中战平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/palacios-late-strike-earns-champions-al-ain-draw-asian-champions-league-2024-09-16/</link><description>周一，卫冕冠军艾因队在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛揭幕战中以 1-1 战平卡塔尔队阿尔萨德队，马蒂亚斯·帕拉西奥斯最后时刻的进球为埃尔南·克雷斯波的球队在改革后的比赛中赢得一分。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 20:51:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/palacios-late-strike-earns-champions-al-ain-draw-asian-champions-league-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>哈萨克斯坦领导人敦促肖尔茨支持中国对乌克兰的和平计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kazakh-leader-urges-scholz-support-chinas-peace-plan-ukraine-2024-09-16/</link><description>哈萨克斯坦总统托卡耶夫周一敦促来访的德国总理肖尔茨放弃俄罗斯可以在战场上被击败的想法，并支持中国对乌克兰的和平计划，但肖尔茨拒绝了这一建议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 16:48:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kazakh-leader-urges-scholz-support-chinas-peace-plan-ukraine-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>顶级商业银行加入七国集团央行主导的数字货币试验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/top-commercial-banks-join-g7-led-central-bank-digital-currency-trial-2024-09-16/</link><description>全球四十家领先的商业银行已加入由七国集团主导的试点计划，该计划与纽约联储以及欧洲、韩国和日本的主要央行合作，推出旨在加速和增强跨境支付的新数字货币平台。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 16:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/top-commercial-banks-join-g7-led-central-bank-digital-currency-trial-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>香港青年传承城市145年火龙舞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/hong-kong-youth-carry-forward-citys-145-year-old-fire-dragon-dance-2024-09-16/</link><description>周一，年轻人走上香港街头，观看具有象征意义的大坑舞火龙，希望为这一有 145 年历史的传统带来新一代。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:27:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/hong-kong-youth-carry-forward-citys-145-year-old-fire-dragon-dance-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织总干事奥孔乔-伊维拉寻求连任以完成“未竟事业”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/wto-chief-okonjo-iweala-tells-reuters-she-will-seek-second-term-2024-09-16/</link><description>世贸组织总干事恩戈齐·奥孔乔-伊韦阿拉将寻求再担任世贸组织总干事四年，此前非洲主导了广泛推动尽早启动这一进程，旨在完成她第一个任期中“未竟的事业”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:06:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/wto-chief-okonjo-iweala-tells-reuters-she-will-seek-second-term-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟称中国电动汽车报价截止日期已过</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-deadline-chinese-ev-price-offers-has-passed-2024-09-16/</link><description>欧盟委员会周一表示，中国电动汽车制造商为避免关税而做出价格承诺的最后期限已经过去，在全部拒绝后，不可能修改其报价。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-deadline-chinese-ev-price-offers-has-passed-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>普京命令俄罗斯军队规模达到150万，成为仅次于中国的第二大军队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putin-orders-russian-army-grow-by-180000-soldiers-become-15-million-strong-2024-09-16/</link><description>俄罗斯总统普京周一下令将俄罗斯军队的常规规模增加18万，达到150万现役军人，此举将使其成为仅次于中国的世界第二大军队。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 12:35:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putin-orders-russian-army-grow-by-180000-soldiers-become-15-million-strong-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>高级议员表示，英国应禁止进口新疆强迫劳动制造的商品</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-should-outlaw-imports-goods-made-by-xinjiang-forced-labour-says-senior-2024-09-16/</link><description>执政党工党的一位高级议员表示，英国应禁止进口中国新疆地区强迫劳动生产的产品，同时重申他呼吁对时尚零售商 Shein 可能在伦敦上市的事宜进行更多审查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 12:03:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-should-outlaw-imports-goods-made-by-xinjiang-forced-labour-says-senior-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>俄新社报道，俄罗斯和中国军舰在“海洋2024”演习中练习导弹发射</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-chinese-warships-practice-missile-firing-ocean-2024-ria-reports-2024-09-16/</link><description>据俄罗斯官方通讯社俄新社周一报道，作为“海洋2024”演习的一部分，俄罗斯太平洋舰队和中国海军的军舰在日本海进行了导弹和火炮射击练习。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 10:24:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-chinese-warships-practice-missile-firing-ocean-2024-ria-reports-2024-09-16/</guid></item><item><title>高盛、花旗集团将中国2024年经济增长预期下调至4.7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/goldman-sachs-citigroup-cut-chinas-2024-growth-forecast-47-2024-09-16/</link><description>在世界第二大经济体8月份工业产出放缓至五个月低点后，高盛和花旗集团已将中国全年经济增长预期下调至4.7%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 05:45:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/goldman-sachs-citigroup-cut-chinas-2024-growth-forecast-47-2024-09-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>